OL,3,CCarer appears in court accused of
OL,4,Ckilling care home resident
OL,6,FA woman has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith manslaughter over the death of a
OL,8,Fcare home resident.
OL,10,FJane Barnard, 65, appeared before
OL,11,FBristol Crown Court accused of killing
OL,12,FDerek Davies, 75, who died on 8
OL,13,FSeptember 2021.
OL,15,FCharges allege that Barnard, of
OL,16,FLonglevens, Gloucester, ill-treated or
OL,17,Fneglected Mr Davies between September
OL,18,F5 and September 9 that year.
