OL,6,FGloucestershire Police previously
OL,7,Fconfirmed that Barnard was working as
OL,8,Fa care worker at Wheatridge Court in
OL,9,FAbbeydale, Gloucester, where Mr Davies
OL,10,Fwas a resident, at the time.
OL,12,FDuring the brief hearing Barnard did
OL,13,Fnot enter any pleas to the two charges
OL,14,Fshe faces.
OL,16,FSam Jones represented the prosecution,
OL,17,Fwhile Jenny Tallentire appeared for
OL,18,Fthe defendant.
