OL,6,FJudge Peter Blair KC, the Recorder of
OL,7,FBristol, adjourned the hearing until
OL,8,FDecember 13 and released Barnard on
OL,9,Funconditional bail.
OL,11,FHe told her: "You must be here for
OL,12,Fthat hearing on December 13.
OL,14,F"You are on unconditional bail but it
OL,15,Fis extremely important you keep in
OL,16,Fclose regular contact with your
OL,17,Fsolicitor and barristers."
